45% snare<br>
25% slow<br>
30 damage<br>
-15 MR<br>
Group Hp Regen<br>
group Mana regen<br>
group Stamina regen<br>
<br>
And all with stringed instruments, I think Denon's also has a spell interrupt but is broken or something.<br>
<br>
</font><P><i><font color='red'>Glom Fyrestormm</font></i><br>
[55 <a href='http://www.graffe.com'>Evoker</a>] <a href='http://www.suckbird.com/roster/profile.asp?who=Glom'>Glom </a>(<a href='http://www.gnomish.net'>Gnome</a>) &lt;<a href='http://www.keepersofthefaith.org'>Keepers of the Faith</a>&gt;<br><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www,kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg BORDER=0></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Sorcerer</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>5/6/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>7:41:31 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://dynamic.gamespy.com/~cazic/cazic/ubb/uploads/grimtoo.jpg  WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Bards job...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I've never worked with a bard doing AE but I have BEEN a bard in AE and the trick is to do several things:<br>
<br>
1) piss off the monsters so bad they ignore everyone else if possible.  Bards are pretty good at this.<br>
2) slow the monsters so that harm is lowered to anyone should stuns be resisted.<br>
3) damage the monsters as best you can.  Bards have a nice line of PBAE DOT songs that aren't as devestating as the Wizard blasts, but are rather impressive.<br>
4) Lower resistances if possible.<br>
5) Pick off stragglers.  It's not worth the mana to blow up 1 guy thats stumbling off smoldering from the catastrophe that befell his friends.  Bards can pick them off well.<br>
<br>
6) oh, and when the fight is over, play mana song and heal song as needed.</font><P><P><i><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www,kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg BORDER=0> at: 5/6/01 8:27:48 pm</FONT><br></i></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.showMessage?topicID=25.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.showMessage?topicID=19.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18.topic&index=5><IMG SRC=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.emailToFriend?topicID=18.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.threadControl?topicID=18.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Topic Control Image"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;Topic Commands (Moderator only)</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=18.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Subscribe</FONT></A>  <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Click to receive email notification of replies</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=18.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Unsubscribe</FONT></A>  <FONT FACE="